      • getIcon

        public static javax.swing.ImageIcon getIcon(java.lang.String imageName)
        Returns the image icon scanning a list of jar files that contain images and if not found finally scanning the file system.
        Parameters:
        imageName - The image path name.
        Returns:
        The ImageIcon or null if the image was not found or an IO exception was thrown.

      • getImage

        public static java.awt.Image getImage(javax.swing.Icon icon)
        Returns an image of the icon. The icon should not use the component passed to the paint method.
        Parameters:
        icon - The icon.
        Returns:
        The image.

      • getImage

        public static java.awt.Image getImage(java.awt.Component component,
                                      javax.swing.Icon icon)
        Returns an image of the icon. The icon should not use the component passed to the paint method.
        Parameters:
        component - The component that hosts the icon.
        icon - The icon.
        Returns:
        The image.
